- if @user.vendor?
  %p 
    Describe the product or service you offer:
    %ul
      %li Tell people what you do
      %li Explain why you love your work
      %li How can people contact you? What's your Web site?

- else 
  %p
    Your bio is first thing people see on your profile. Some ideas:
    %ul
      %li Describe your sense of style
      %li Explain what you love about life.
      %li What's the last thing you purchased for a friend?